## Complete Checklist

Before considering your syncable entity complete, verify ALL items:

### Syncable Entity Requirements
- [ ] TypeORM entity extends `SyncableEntity`
- [ ] Entity has `isCustom` boolean column
- [ ] Entity-to-flat transform sets `universalIdentifier` correctly (generated with `v4()`)

### JSONB Properties (if applicable)
- [ ] All JSONB columns wrapped with `JsonbProperty<T>`
- [ ] Foreign keys in JSONB use `SerializedRelation` type
- [ ] JSONB structure types properly defined

### Registration (twenty-shared)
- [ ] Metadata name added to `ALL_METADATA_NAME`

### Flat Entity Definition
- [ ] Flat entity type defined using `FlatEntityFrom<T>`
- [ ] Flat entity maps type defined
- [ ] Editable properties constant defined

### Central Constants Registration
- [ ] Registered in `AllFlatEntityTypesByMetadataName`
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_ENTITY_PROPERTIES_CONFIGURATION_BY_METADATA_NAME`
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_UNIVERSAL_METADATA_RELATIONS`
- [ ] Registered in `ALL_METADATA_REQUIRED_METADATA_FOR_VALIDATION`

### Cache Layer
- [ ] Cache service created with `@WorkspaceCache` decorator
- [ ] Cache key matches `flat{EntityName}Maps` pattern
- [ ] Cache uses `withDeleted: true`
- [ ] Flat entity module created and exports cache service

### Transform Utilities
- [ ] Create transform utility created
- [ ] Update transform utility created
- [ ] String properties sanitized
- [ ] Foreign keys extracted before sanitization
- [ ] Foreign keys resolved to universal identifiers
- [ ] Transform utils return universal flat entities

### Migration Builder
- [ ] Action types defined (universal + flat)
- [ ] Validator service created
- [ ] Validator **never throws** - returns errors array
- [ ] Validator **never mutates** entity maps
- [ ] Builder service extends `WorkspaceEntityMigrationBuilderService`
- [ ] Builder creates actions with universal entities

### Orchestrator Wiring (⚠️ CRITICAL)
- [ ] **Builder imported in orchestrator**
- [ ] **Builder injected in orchestrator constructor**
- [ ] **Builder called in `buildWorkspaceMigration`**
- [ ] **Actions added to orchestrator return statement**

### Migration Runner
- [ ] Create action handler implemented
- [ ] Update action handler implemented
- [ ] Delete action handler implemented
- [ ] Create handler implements `transpileUniversalActionToFlatAction`
- [ ] Update handler implements `transpileUniversalActionToFlatAction`
- [ ] Delete handler implements `transpileUniversalActionToFlatAction`
- [ ] Create handler uses `insertFlatEntitiesInRepository`
- [ ] Universal-to-flat conversion utility created

### Module Registration
- [ ] Builder registered in builder module (providers + exports)
- [ ] Validator registered in validators module (providers + exports)
- [ ] All 3 action handlers registered in action handlers module (providers)

### Testing
- [ ] Integration tests created
- [ ] Successful CRUD scenarios tested
- [ ] Failing validation scenarios tested

